1	/* ============================================================
2	 * dAIly digest — magazine stylesheet
3	 *
4	 * Editorial print register layered on Anthropic.com/news's clean
5	 * structural foundation. Display: Bodoni Moda (variable optical-size
6	 * didone). Body: Hanken Grotesk (humanist grotesque). Warm cream paper,
7	 * near-black ink, weathered newsprint-red accent. Why-it-matters runs
8	 * as a continuation italic with an inline red flag — no zoning.
9	 *
10	 * LAYOUT — magazine front:
11	 *   Masthead → Signal epigraph → Featured row (featured + Old Gold aside)
12	 *   → Front meta line → Grid (first item spans cols) → Old Gold archive
13	 *   pocket → Colophon.
14	 *
15	 * TYPOGRAPHY RULE (load-bearing — read before changing anything):
16	 *   Bodoni Moda is ONLY used at sizes ≥ 2rem OR as single-glyph
17	 *   decoration. Didone's thin-thick contrast collapses at smaller
18	 *   sizes and makes real reading hard. Everywhere else is Hanken.
19	 *   Four Bodoni usages survive this rule:
20	 *     1. .title (wordmark — logo territory)
